22:15.519 --> 22:18.480
I didn't realize
they would be ready today!

22:18.559 --> 22:19.880
So crazy about them!

22:20.319 --> 22:23.119
I don't know where I see myself
in a few years.

22:23.240 --> 22:26.160
I hope I'll still be doing this
and that my brand

22:26.240 --> 22:28.720
will reach much higher goals and results.

22:28.960 --> 22:33.119
I hope that my family grows bigger
and that everything will be fine.

22:33.759 --> 22:36.079
-I wanna take a photo like this.
-Tell us.

22:36.160 --> 22:38.000
Here we have

22:38.839 --> 22:43.240
-merino wool and cashmere.
-So pretty! May I? So beautiful.

22:43.319 --> 22:44.960
-Everything...
-A fabulous hand.

22:45.160 --> 22:46.480
