23:15.279 --> 23:17.200
I feel good, I feel fit.

23:19.400 --> 23:23.039
-I didn't realize they were ready.
-Sure.

23:23.200 --> 23:26.000
-I thought we'd go through the designs.
-No.

23:26.319 --> 23:30.160
-No, it's time to see them in real life.
-Great! Cool!

23:30.559 --> 23:32.720
With this pregnancy, I get to work,

23:32.799 --> 23:34.960
I can still see my friends and so on.

23:35.039 --> 23:36.240
It's a plus, really.

