-The jaw is more...
-She's got a long face.

24:39.960 --> 24:41.839
-It's not true, love.
-You think?

24:41.920 --> 24:47.799
I always try to look
at the bright side of things.

24:49.200 --> 24:52.359
-Look at those cute lips!
