27:46.039 --> 27:48.519
A moustache for daddy!

27:48.599 --> 27:51.359
I think he sees in Leo
many of his passions.

27:51.920 --> 27:53.119
Can you do that?

27:54.160 --> 27:55.519
-Very well done!
-Well done!

27:59.839 --> 28:02.359
